Package org.neo4j.cypher.operations

Class PathValueBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.cypher.operations.PathValueBuilder
  • public class PathValueBuilder
extends Object
    Builder for building paths from generated code, used when the length of the path is not known at compile time.

    NOTE: this class is designed to be easy-to-use from generated code rather than from code typed by more or less anthropic beings, so refactor with some care.
